        SpatialReference getBest()

        Returns:

      • getBestAccuracy

        int getBestAccuracy()
        A whole number that informs of the precision with which the projection has been identified. When the number is lower, the accuracy is greater . Zero indicates that the projection has been identified exactly.
        Returns:
